{"search_data": "JharkhandJharkhand Mukhyamantri Krishi Ashirwad Yojana Benefits in September \u2013 CM Jharkhand Mukhyamantri Krishi Ashirwad Yojana benefits to reach around 35 lakh farmers in September 2019, Rs. 5,000 per acre into bank accounts of farmers with landholdings upto 5 acre through DBT mode to purchase seeds, fertilizers, agriculture equipment etc \u0939\u093f\u0902\u0926\u0940 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092a\u0922\u093c\u0947\u0902Jharkhand Mukhyamantri Krishi Ashirwad Yojana Benefits in SeptAll the small and marginal farmers whose land holdings are upto 5 acres will get Jharkhand Mukhyamantri Krishi Ashirwad Yojana Benefits in the month of September. The monetary assistance of Rs. 5,000 per acre could be used to purchase seeds, pesticides, agricultural equipment etc. Now farmers would be made self reliant through this scheme and they will not have to borrow money at higher interest rates from the open market.This CM Krishi Aashirwad Yojana would run in parallel to the PM Kisan Scheme of the central government. Now all the farmers would get Rs. 2,000 per acre per annum in 3 equal installments apart from Rs. 5,000 per acre. CM has already asked deputy commissioners of all 24 districts to run campaign to connect 51 lakh farmers with this scheme. DCs will hold meetings with Mukhiyas and panchayat representatives in their respective districts and will update details of land holdings in villages.Jharkhand govt. Steps for Women EmpowermentWomen Empowerment is one of the topmost priorities of the state govt. and around 1.90 lakh sakhi mandals have already been constituted since 2014. Through sakhi mandals, govt. is providing various employment opportunities to women. CM also tells that the property registration fees of value upto Rs. 50 lakh is Rs. 1 for women. To strengthen Sakhi Mandals, the state govt. has allocated Rs. 500 crore.Despite being a mineral rich state, people of Jharkhand remained poor. In the past 4 years, govt. has taken various efforts to improve economic condition of poor and upliftment of living standards of people. CM said that in the next 5 years, these efforts will gain momentum.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: https://www.dailypioneer.com/2019/state-editions/farmers-to-get-benefit-of-ashirwad-yojna-in-sept--cm.html  at  "}